# lore_skeleton_npc_token [9001]
#
You discover a tattered banner, crudely fashioned.  Upon grasping
hold of it, you sense the presence of a skeleton nearby that responds
to your mental control.  You find you can issue the following commands
to your skeletal unit:

   ADMIT, ATTACK, BANNER, BEHIND, CONTACT, DEFAULT, DEFEND, DROP,
   EXECUTE, FLAG, GIVE, HOSTILE, MOVE, NAME, NEUTRAL, PILLAGE,
   PROMOTE, RAZE, SEEK, STACK, STOP, TAKE, TERRORIZE, UNSTACK, WAIT
